Dear Hiring Team,

I am writing to express my interest in the *Cloud Engineer* role with *Client*. I bring over three years of experience building and operating production systems across cloud architecture, CI/CD pipelines, observability workflows, and security-focused multi-tenant backend platforms, along with a Master of Science in Computer Science from Pace University.

