That background has shaped the way I work: I build with security, automation, and operational discipline from the start. I am comfortable using observability to detect issues early, using CI/CD to deploy safely, and using cloud primitives to keep systems reliable under load. I would welcome the opportunity to contribute that mindset to *Client* as it builds secure, compliant, and cost-conscious cloud platforms with strong engineering standards, *availability* goals, and practical collaboration across technical and business stakeholders.

Sincerely,
Osaid Khan

